WEBVTT

00:14:28.531 --> 00:14:30.574
or that are not bioequivalent.

00:14:31.282 --> 00:14:34.280
As the FDA investigator
Peter Baker put it,

00:14:34.891 --> 00:14:37.580
if people actually understood,

00:14:38.373 --> 00:14:40.739
then nobody
would take these drugs.

00:14:41.799 --> 00:14:44.820
Are there ways to solve
this global problem?

00:14:44.844 --> 00:14:46.293
Yes, there are.

00:14:47.000 --> 00:14:49.374
Solutions begin with recognizing

00:14:49.398 --> 00:14:53.021
that our current honor system
for drug regulation

00:14:53.045 --> 00:14:55.995
is a relic of a bygone age.

00:14:56.019 --> 00:14:58.943
Science evolves. Medicine evolves.

00:14:58.967 --> 00:15:01.362
The global economy evolves.